{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1f90677f69","title":"给田家英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ceb30c3378","index":0,"year":1951,"month":4,"day":16,"articleId":"1f90677f69"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"6fc362153a","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"田家英，当时任毛泽东的秘书，参加了《毛泽东选集》的编辑工作。"},{"id":"46f60d3e02","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长，参加了《毛泽东选集》的编辑工作。"},{"id":"edd3e707f4","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这4篇文章，后来都收入了《毛泽东选集》。前两篇收入《毛泽东选集》第二卷，题目为《和英国记者贝特兰的谈话》《和中央社、扫荡报、新民报三记者的谈话》。《一个极其重要的政策》收入《毛泽东选集》第三卷。第四篇收入《毛泽东选集》第四卷，题目为《全世界革命力量团结起来，反对帝国主义的侵略》"}],"contents":[{"id":"b6d99f2bc7","type":"title","text":"给田家英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69"},{"id":"6fc362153a","type":"paragraph","text":"家英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69"},{"id":"46f60d3e02","type":"paragraph","text":"此九篇请送陈值达叫同志阅后付排改正。其中，和英国记者谈话，和中央社等记者谈话，一个极其重要的政策，全世界革命力量团结起来等四篇，我已照原件修改，请即照此改正，新送来这四件稿子我就不必看了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69"},{"id":"edd3e707f4","type":"paragraph","text":"以上这些及昨付第二次看过的一大批，都可付翻译——惟其中的一篇，即《并冈山的斗争》，请送来再看一次。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69"},{"id":"c42fdb4e0a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"1f90677f69"},{"id":"8352c73959","type":"paragraph","tex